OL,6,FHowever, visa issues and the Cold
OL,7,FWar's Iron Curtain meant the game
OL,8,Fnever went ahead.
OL,10,FFast forward to 2025 and fans
OL,11,Ftravelled by plane, train and even
OL,12,Fbike to witness the game first-hand.
OL,14,FLurgan became a sea of purple as more
OL,15,Fthan one thousand fans of the German
OL,16,Fclub made the trip and could be heard
OL,17,Fin fine voice as they marched their
OL,18,Fway to Mourneview Park.
