OL,6,FGlenavon manager Paddy McLaughlin
OL,7,Fsaid: "An unbelievable day. Full
OL,8,Fcredit to everyone involved. A
OL,9,Fbrilliant day out for everyone, for
OL,10,Fboth clubs.
OL,12,F"They came over in their numbers...
OL,13,Fand it made it an unbelievable
OL,14,Foccasion for Glenavon football club.
OL,16,F"Absolutely delighted to be part of
OL,17,Fit. We can do nothing but thank the
OL,18,Fboys for coming over and making it a
OL,19,Fspecial occasion."
