OL,6,FCaptain Barney McKeown said: "The
OL,7,Fatmosphere they brought was brilliant.
OL,9,F"It gives us a bit of a taste of what
OL,10,FEuropean football could be like.
OL,12,F"As much as pre-season isn't really
OL,13,Fabout results, more about
OL,14,Fperformances, we certainly got a
OL,15,Fperformance out of it that we were
OL,16,Fpleased with and it's something to
OL,17,Fbuild on."
OL,19,FIt wasn't to be Glenavon's day,
OL,20,Ffalling to a 2-0 defeat and a 7-0 loss
OL,21,Foverall on aggregate.
